h in London. Works are also exhibited in Des Moines Art Center, Iowa, and Centro de Arte Moderna, Lisbon.</p><p><strong>2014</strong> – Present:Peter is elected Honorary Member of the Royal Birmingham Society of Arts. His work is shown at the Tate Modern and Barbican Centre in London, Thyssen-Bornemisza in Madrid and featured in China’s Vogue Magazine. He currently travels and works between Central America, Europe, and Australia.</p>\n\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column_inner][/et_pb_row_inner][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_4"][et_pb_image _builder_version="3.0.62" src="http://peterphillips.kbbdeveloper.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/photo3.jpg" show_in_lightbox="off" url_new_window="off" use_overlay="off" sticky="off" align="left" always_center_on_mobile="on" border_style="solid" force_fullwidth="off" /][et_pb_text _builder_version="3.0.62" background_layout="light" text_orientation="left" border_style="solid"]\n\n<p style="text-align: center;">Laing and Phillips with Hybrid</p>\n\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_image _builder_version="3.0.62" src="http://peterphillips.kbbdeveloper.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/photo4.jpg" show_in_lightbox="off" url_new_window="off" use_overlay="off" sticky="off" align="left" always_center_on_mobile="on" border_style="solid" force_fullwidth="off" /][et_pb_text _builder_version="3.0.62" background_layout="light" text_orientation="left" border_style="solid"]\n\n<p style="text-align: center;">At exhibition with Roy Lichtenstain</p>\n\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_image _builder_version="3.0.62" src="http://peterphillips.kbbdeveloper.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/photo1.jpg" show_in_lightbox="off" url_new_window="off" use_overlay="off" sticky="off" align="left" always_center_on_mobile="on" border_style="solid" force_fullwidth="off" /][et_pb_text _builder_version="3.0.62" background_layout="light" text_orientation="left" border_style="solid"]\n\n<p style="text-align: center;">Phillips &amp; Bruno Bischofsberger</p>\n\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_image _builder_v